body: Only good ones are the 1st and last stories. The rest are bad visually and no where near as pleasing.

@GreesyNinja
Nope, not exclusive. It's a collection from different books. I know the story from page 91-112 with the blonde girl. It's a chapter from the hentai book "Honey Blonde" by Fukudahda. It's a great hentai, but it's old, like 10 years or so. I'm pretty sure none of this stuff is actually "new". This collection is from 2015, but all of it's content is probably just taken from older hentai books.
are these works exclusive to this magazine?
